<h3 id="thermal-evaporator">Thermal Evaporator</h3>
<p>Capable of depositing a wide range of materials (organics, Au, Cu, Cr, Al, Ag, dielectrics), with up to 3 simultaneous sources on up to 6‚Äù wafers.</p>
<figure>
  <p><img src="/images/infrapic/Evaporator 1.jpg" width="60%" />
<img src="/images/infrapic/Evaporator 2.jpg" width="60%" /></p>
</figure>

