<h3 id="ultrafast-spectroscopy">Ultrafast spectroscopy</h3>
<p>10W femtosecond Yb:KGW amplifier with optical parametric amplifier, pulse compressor, transient absorption spectroscopy and microscopy, electronically delayed pump-probe, time-resolved photoluminescence (streak camera), spectrally tunable Z-scan and cryostat.</p>
<figure>
  <p><img src="/images/infrapic/ultrafast.jpg" width="60%" /></p>
</figure>
